    <item>
      <title>Docs: Unity Version</title>
      <link>https://vrm.dev/en/docs/univrm/install/unity_version/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2020 17:19:08 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://vrm.dev/en/docs/univrm/install/unity_version/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2 id=&#34;univrm-0800-&#34;&gt;UniVRM-0.80.0 ～&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have discontinued support for Unity-2018.4LTS and updated the development version to Unity-2019.4LTS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Unity Version&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Note&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Unity-2019.4 LTS&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Current UniVRM development version&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Unity-2020.4 LTS&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Current version for UniVRM UPM testing&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Unity-2021&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Please report any issues to &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vrm-c/UniVRM/issues&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;univrm-0560--0790&#34;&gt;UniVRM-0.56.0 ～ 0.79.0&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support &lt;code&gt;Unity-2018.4&lt;/code&gt; and above. &lt;code&gt;Unity-2019.4 LTS&lt;/code&gt; is recommended.&lt;/p&gt;
